</li>
<li><a href="http://symptoms.webmd.com/coresc/landing?condition=091e9c5e808e8203&amp;bpid[0]=24&amp;sid[0]=105&amp;bpid[1]=24&amp;sid[1]=451" onclick="return sl(this, '', 'sc-symindex-cmb_1');">Ascaris worms</a><p>Ascarisis is an infection by a roundworm, and can cause visible worms in the stool and respiratory symptoms.</p>
</li>
<li class="bg"><a href="http://symptoms.webmd.com/coresc/landing?condition=091e9c5e808e8078&amp;bpid[0]=24&amp;sid[0]=105&amp;bpid[1]=24&amp;sid[1]=451" onclick="return sl(this, '', 'sc-symindex-cmb_1');">Irritable bowel syndrome</a><p>Irritable bowel syndrome is a common condition that causes painful spasms and cramping in the large intestine.</p>
</li>
<li><a href="http://symptoms.webmd.com/coresc/landing?condition=091e9c5e808e7ba6&amp;bpid[0]=24&amp;sid[0]=105&amp;bpid[1]=24&amp;sid[1]=451" onclick="return sl(this, '', 'sc-symindex-cmb_1');">Gastroenteritis</a><p>Gastroenteritis is inflammation of the stomach and intestine that causes diarrhea and vomiting.</p>
</li>
<li class="bg"><a href="http://symptoms.webmd.com/coresc/landing?condition=091e9c5e808e7bef&amp;bpid[0]=24&amp;sid[0]=105&amp;bpid[1]=24&amp;sid[1]=451" onclick="return sl(this, '', 'sc-symindex-cmb_1');">Lactose intolerance</a><p>Lactose intolerance, or the inability to digest lactose, leads to gas, bloating, and other symptoms.</p>
